\section{Introduction}
Job interviews remain one of the most stressful experiences for candidates, with studies showing that 92\% of job seekers experience anxiety before interviews. Traditional mock interview methods lack objective feedback, personalization, and scalability. \textbf{InterviewMate AI} bridges this gap by providing an intelligent, AI-driven platform that simulates real interview scenarios with comprehensive analytics.

\section{Problem Statement}
\begin{enumerate}[leftmargin=*]
    \item Lack of personalized interview preparation tools
    \item No objective measurement of non-verbal communication (facial expressions, tone)
    \item Inability to track progress over time with quantifiable metrics
    \item Limited access to company-specific and role-specific questions
    \item Absence of real-time feedback during practice sessions
\end{enumerate}

\section{Proposed Solution}
InterviewMate AI provides:
\begin{itemize}
    \item \textbf{Smart Question Generation} based on resume parsing and job profiles
    \item \textbf{Multi-modal Emotion Analysis} (face + voice + text)
    \item \textbf{Real-time Confidence Scoring} with weighted factors
    \item \textbf{STAR Model Evaluation} for structured answers
    \item \textbf{Progress Dashboard} with trend analysis and improvement recommendations
\end{itemize}

\section{System Architecture}
The platform follows a 3-tier architecture:
\begin{enumerate}
    \item \textbf{Presentation Layer:} React.js SPA with WebRTC for video/audio
    \item \textbf{Application Layer:} Python Flask REST API with AI microservices
    \item \textbf{Data Layer:} MySQL (relational data) + MongoDB (unstructured data)
\end{enumerate}

\section{Key Features}
\begin{table}[h]
\centering
\begin{tabular}{@{}lll@{}}
\toprule
\textbf{Feature} & \textbf{Technology} & \textbf{Output} \\
\midrule
Face Emotion Detection & OpenCV + CNN (FER2013) & Confidence/Nervousness Score \\
Speech Emotion Recognition & Librosa + SVM/RF & Vocal Stress/Enthusiasm Score \\
Speech-to-Text & Whisper API / Vosk & Transcript + Filler Word Count \\
NLP Analysis & spaCy + NLTK + Transformers & Grammar, Relevance, STAR Score \\
Eye Contact Tracking & MediaPipe Face Mesh & Eye Contact Percentage \\
Confidence Scoring & Weighted Aggregation & Overall 0-100 Score \\
\bottomrule
\end{tabular}
\end{table}

\section{Expected Outcomes}
\begin{itemize}
    \item 40-60\% improvement in candidate confidence scores after 5 sessions
    \item Objective identification of weakest areas (communication, technical knowledge, body language)
    \item Company-specific preparation with 500+ curated questions
    \item Exportable PDF reports for sharing with mentors/career counselors
\end{itemize}

